<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>[سورة المعارج <span class="c2">(٧٠)</span> : الآيات ١٤ الى ٢٠]<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>وَمَنْ فِي الْأَرْضِ جَمِيعاً ثُمَّ يُنْجِيهِ <span class="c2">(١٤)</span> كَلاَّ إِنَّها لَظى <span class="c2">(١٥)</span> نَزَّاعَةً لِلشَّوى <span class="c2">(١٦)</span> تَدْعُوا مَنْ أَدْبَرَ وَتَوَلَّى <span class="c2">(١٧)</span> وَجَمَعَ فَأَوْعى <span class="c2">(١٨)</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>إِنَّ الْإِنْسانَ خُلِقَ هَلُوعاً <span class="c2">(١٩)</span> إِذا مَسَّهُ الشَّرُّ جَزُوعاً <span class="c2">(٢٠)</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>١٤-<span class="c5"> وَمَنْ فِي الْأَرْضِ جَمِيعاً ثُمَّ يُنْجِيهِ:</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>ثُمَّ يُنْجِيهِ هذا الفداء.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>١٥-<span class="c5"> كَلَّا إِنَّها لَظى:</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>كَلَّا ردع.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>إِنَّها أي النار.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>لَظى لهب خالص.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>١٦-<span class="c5"> نَزَّاعَةً لِلشَّوى:</span><a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>نَزَّاعَةً شديدة النزع.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>لِلشَّوى لليدين والرجلين وسائر الأطراف.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>١٧-<span class="c5"> تَدْعُوا مَنْ أَدْبَرَ وَتَوَلَّى:</span><a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>تَدْعُوا تنادى.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>مَنْ أَدْبَرَ من أعرض عن الحق.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>وَتَوَلَّى وترك الطاعة.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>١٨-<span class="c5"> وَجَمَعَ فَأَوْعى:</span><a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>وَجَمَعَ المال.<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>فَأَوْعى وجعله فى وعائه- خزائنه- ومنع حق الله تعالى.<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>١٩-<span class="c5"> إِنَّ الْإِنْسانَ خُلِقَ هَلُوعاً:</span><a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>خُلِقَ طبع.<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span>هَلُوعاً شديد الهلع والفزع.<a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p23"></span>٢٠-<span class="c5"> إِذا مَسَّهُ الشَّرُّ جَزُوعاً:</span><a href="#p23" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p24"></span>الشَّرُّ المكروه والعسر.<a href="#p24" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p25"></span>جَزُوعاً شديد الجزع.<a href="#p25" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>